{"title":"电子管工人心向党","authors":["顾顺章"],"dates":[{"year":1968,"month":5,"day":1}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"电子管工人心向党"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"顾顺章"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱每天上工去战斗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红色宝书握在手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"请示伟大导师毛主席，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"话儿领着心儿走。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"油一滴滴流，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"滋润着齿轮、车轴……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"语录一句句读，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"使咱心胸开阔，放眼全球！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"车轮在飞转，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"产品如水流，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每只电子管，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"连着五大洲。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"电子管工人心向党，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"传播毛泽东思想永不休！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“抓革命，促生产”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席的教导记心头。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乘风破浪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"靠毛泽东思想拨正航向；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"攻克尖端，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"靠毛泽东思想指挥战斗！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东思想传到那里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那里就掀起革命风暴；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席的每一个号令，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都使帝修反浑身发抖！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红色宝书握在手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"话儿领着心儿走；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"步步紧跟毛主席，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红彤彤的太阳照全球！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":5,"page_end":5}